      public VideoBoxModel​(Video video, java.lang.String username, int width, int height)
      This constructor creates the model for the videoBox element
      Parameters:
      video - The video entity retrieved from the DB.
      username - The username of the student that is currently watchg the video
      width - The width of the image of the video panel.
      height - The height of the image of the video panel.

    • VideoBoxModel

      public VideoBoxModel​(Video video)
      this constructor is meant to be used when the videobox controller is created by statisticsPaneView. It won't use the username of the student that is currently watching the video and it will use default width and height to create the video panel.
